Good idea, poor execution. You can't set your radius for further than 150mi, get notifications for multiple locations, or search by date, so it's really only useful for checking what local bar bands are playing tonight - bands 'in town' isn't just a cute name. If you're the type to make a weekend trip to see a band you like, or live somewhere like the northeast corridor where taking a 150+ mile train ride to a show isn't unusual, it probably won't do what you want. Which is a shame, because it's a great app idea and an excellent interface.
